Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.78,0:00:17.33,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}Follow me Follow you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.12,0:00:29.71,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}傷を負った　世界を知った
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.42,0:00:34.68,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}強く儚い果実
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.80,0:00:41.64,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}つきまとう　責任の重たさで
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.93,0:00:46.10,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}熟れ落ちて　土へと還る
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.48,0:00:49.02,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}Follow me Follow you　痛みでさえ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.07,0:00:51.78,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}Follow me Follow you　通じ合えば
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.90,0:00:56.03,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}この血の滾りを解放してけ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.03,0:00:57.03,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}そこにいますか？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.12,0:01:01.91,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}衝突に戦々恐々　降り立つ堕天使
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.41,0:01:07.17,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}早々に早熟な実も　食らい尽くすの？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.79,0:01:12.92,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}もがく度に　蒼穹に聴いた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.09,0:01:16.09,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}君を確かめた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.09,0:01:16.92,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}あっけない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.92,0:01:20.72,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}無い無い　馴れ合い　有り余った慟哭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.26,0:01:26.10,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}葛藤に混乱していく　今を生きて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.35,0:01:32.94,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)\pos(960,3)}それでもまだ　僕らは目指した
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.90,0:01:34.49,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)\fs45\pos(960,54)}Follow me Follow you　痛みでさえ
